smartmeter-datacollector-configurator (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * frontend: upgrade to Vue 3 with Vite; upgrade to node 22 (LTS)
  * frontend: replace axios with native fetch API
  * frontend: update all dependencies to latest major versions
  * frontend: add VSE RL-DSP standardization checkbox and topic group field
  * backend: add new MQTT sink type 'mqttrldsp' with topic_group field
  * backend: set default Python version to 3.13 (debian trixie)
  * backend: update Python dependencies

